****************************************

BRIEF DESCRIPTION:

Converting roman numeral numbers into its decimal (base 10) equivalent

****************************************

COMPILATION:

cobc -x -free -Wall romanA3_1.cob conv.cob

****************************************

EXECUTION:

./romanA3_1

****************************************

RUNTIME:

			   Roman Number Equivalents
                    *Enter Q or quit to exit the program*
*Enter a roman numeral (upper or lower case) to convert to its decimal equivalent*
 
 --------------------------------------------
         Roman Number             Dec. Equiv.
 ------------------------------   -----------
X
 X                                       10
XI
 XI                                      11
ix
 ix                                       9
VII
 VII                                      7
 
****************************************
